Jonathan Corbet wrote:
> I can't be accused, however, of having spent too much time thinking through
> how an implementation would actually be done...
Your scheme sounds very much like a variant on the PAL mechanism
of UNICOS. The PAL mechanism was implemented as an extension of
the POSIX capability mechanism at Cray.
